description: Rustic Frames Perfect for the Great Outdoors This rugged yet beautiful reclaimed wood frame gets its name from the world-famous city and ski resort that helped host the Winter 2002 Olympics. Park City is rustic romance in every sense of the word, and this beautiful barnwood frame is intended to represent the spirit and beauty of this beautiful mountain retreat. Handcrafted from aged reclaimed wood, with a dark-walnut-stained alder inset, this frame is available in several sizes and also has an option that comes with metal corner brackets for a little bit more industrial look.
